Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the volume when the pedal is at minimum position.

Parameters.name: Max
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the volume when the pedal is at maximum position.

description: This sound, which uses EBH360, is good for slapping.

FX.name: MB Comp
FX.description: This is a simulation of the MultiComp (MODE:MB).

Parameters.name: Comp
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the depth of the compression.

Parameters.name: LoTHR
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the threshold that triggers the low-frequency effect.

Parameters.name: HiTHR
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the threshold that triggers the high-frequency effect.

FX.name: EBH360
FX.description: This models the sound of the EBS HD360 bass amplifier.

Parameters.name: MID-F
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the center frequency of the mid-range.

FX.name: ZNR
FX.description: ZOOM's unique noise reduction cuts noise during pauses in playing without affecting the tone.

Parameters.name: Depth
Parameters.explanation: Sets the depth of noise reduction.

FX.name: EB4x10TW
FX.description: This models an EBS ProLine 410 cabinet with four 10" speakers and a tweeter.

Parameters.name: DYN20
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts volume of the Electro-Voice RE-20.

Parameters.name: DYN57
Parameters.explanation: This adjusts the volume of the modeled sound captured from the tweeter by a Shure SM57.

Parameters.name: BAL
Parameters.explanation: Adjusts the balance between original and effect sounds.

FX.name: High EQ
FX.description: Designed for high frequencies, this equalizer allows you to select the type.

Parameters.name: FREQ
Parameters.explanation: Sets the frequency of the filter.

Parameters.name: Gain
Parameters.explanation:
Adjusts the gain. 
This setting is disabled when the Type parameter is set to LPF.
